text: Pakpattan is a city in Punjab, Pakistan. Pakpattan may also refer to: *Pakpattan District, a district of Punjab (Pakistan) *Pakpattan Tehsil, a tehsil of district Pakpattan ==See also== *Pakpattan railway station, a railway station in Pakistan *Pakpattan Canal, canal in Pakistan *Pakpatan Hydropower Project, a small hydropower project in Pakistan * *
